Our branches and corporate banking centres are staffed by the best and brightest people who will take an active role in their neighbourhood, because we believe that no one understands Victorians like the people who live here.

Our Opportunity - Customer Service Advisor

At Bank of Melbourne, we believe in taking the time to get to know our customers as a person, not a series of accounts. We're looking for people who genuinely enjoy dealing with people to be key members of our local branch customer service team.

Our Customer Service Advisors’ have a unique ability; they know how to make banking more of a conversation so customers actually look forward to coming into the branch. They know our customers' names and the neighbourhood they work in like the back of their hand, so they're always assured of a friendly face. Understanding the individual needs of both our personal and business owner customers is second nature and they're able to recommend exactly which products and services will genuinely serve them best. Firstly, you want different, not traditional. You love the challenge of working in a dynamic environment where you're setting a new benchmark in customer service.

Where to from here?
